::Aerotaur::
       He eyes Empath cautiously, sizing her up as soon as she enters the 
room.  He glances at Ragnar.  "She knows of what she speaks.  You would be 
wise to listen."  He stands up and walks out into the hall casting a wary 
glance at Empath as he passes her.  He slowly makes his way toward the bridge 
hoping to find something to do.

--part1_13.13bf80a9.2ae75c98_boundary
